ote":{"pid":"a4addf545e9db5512d8e9ac2640872ba7ac4cc87","tid":1013492,"uid":8257,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:08:09.000Z","msg":"得2萬零一個月 不過要求應該非常高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:45:39.000Z","msg":"2萬喺HKD定USD?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:47:57.000Z","msg":"HKD <br />\n如果2萬幾美金月薪 同總領事同級咁滯喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:51:59.000Z","msg":"有冇得加人工㗎?<br />\n如果唔係，長遠嚟講係好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ec1405f8b67097051aac8c58b8f664b6c0dd40","tid":1013492,"uid":16873,"like":88,"dislike":1,"score":87,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:52:29.000Z","msg":"給美軍帶路的步驟：<br />\n<br />\n一、準備工作：<br />\n<br />\n1、見到美軍來了，要趕快圍上去表示善意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-6r9elCjWa2U/V4OgM8rf_4I/AAAAAAAABFw/WZYjCWFBdgM2R3yy03cGkbt0NK101PvNACLcB/s1600/640.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-6r9elCjWa2U%2FV4OgM8rf_4I%2FAAAAAAAABFw%2FWZYjCWFBdgM2R3yy03cGkbt0NK101PvNACLcB%2Fs1600%2F640.jpeg&h=2f72c98b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2、與美軍拉家常，比如問他你叫什麼名？ 家裡幾口人？ 養了幾條狗？ 結婚了嗎？ 軍隊收入怎麼樣?要讓大兵感受到生活的不公平和專政。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hhKbYF1hIIc/V4OgvkZCXtI/AAAAAAAABF0/mFFp4u_FM2wWB19CCtq800f0aMWEWDgJgCLcB/s1600/641.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-hhKbYF1hIIc%2FV4OgvkZCXtI%2FAAAAAAAABF0%2FmFFp4u_FM2wWB19CCtq800f0aMWEWDgJgCLcB%2Fs1600%2F641.jpeg&h=3132a268&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3、等於大兵熟悉了環境，幫助破除埋伏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-dufloBncI3A/V4Og7-fcF6I/AAAAAAAABF8/7T5P19yq9TQl-PrDSiLs6kqgNL5HcnXFQCLcB/s1600/642.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-dufloBncI3A%2FV4Og7-fcF6I%2FAAAAAAAABF8%2F7T5P19yq9TQl-PrDSiLs6kqgNL5HcnXFQCLcB%2Fs1600%2F642.jpeg&h=12c5e4a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二 、 指路：<br />\n <br />\n 1、 如果你不想帶路可以從地圖上指出重要目標地點之類的信息<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-5W8NcZoxXZQ/V4OiDO9JjvI/AAAAAAAABGI/T8AYVJf9wo4ZZ76jl0JAy9FYzQHXKwXtACLcB/s1600/643.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-5W8NcZoxXZQ%2FV4OiDO9JjvI%2FAAAAAAAABGI%2FT8AYVJf9wo4ZZ76jl0JAy9FYzQHXKwXtACLcB%2Fs1600%2F643.jpeg&h=a1a804b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三、帶路：<br />\n<br />\n1、以上所有的行動都是為了這一刻的到來，平時苦練的follow me，this way為的就是這一刻。 帶他去暴政辦公地，武力鎮壓處，非正常關押處。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-w24uTcJAFvw/V4OjFrdHNTI/AAAAAAAABGU/awGKtJqSaZ0bbWuWycrhvRmPqrV9lr4vgCLcB/s1600/644.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-w24uTcJAFvw%2FV4OjFrdHNTI%2FAAAAAAAABGU%2FawGKtJqSaZ0bbWuWycrhvRmPqrV9lr4vgCLcB%2Fs1600%2F644.jpeg&h=f1a02c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2、英語練的好，帶路帶到老。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-o03XzzNetfw/V4OjSJVv9jI/AAAAAAAABGY/HCnZHi7vxFQ9KkvSfzaMnu5EkD-ymaK1gCLcB/s1600/645.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-o03XzzNetfw%2FV4OjSJVv9jI%2FAAAAAAAABGY%2FHCnZHi7vxFQ9KkvSfzaMnu5EkD-ymaK1gCLcB%2Fs1600%2F645.jpeg&h=c7e640a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3、This Way.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-4K2_bAD_NpQ/V4OjgheNLAI/AAAAAAAABGc/Ymmoz4HXdQ4yxA80z9uKRNwB_iVE9XyOQCLcB/s1600/646.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-4K2_bAD_NpQ%2FV4OjgheNLAI%2FAAAAAAAABGc%2FYmmoz4HXdQ4yxA80z9uKRNwB_iVE9XyOQCLcB%2Fs1600%2F646.jpeg&h=91656967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4、 Over There. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-neh7haio0ZA/V4Okf-cfm8I/AAAAAAAABGs/tgDJnGJP7kQObdMY8bHUiZTMv8i_1YRrgCLcB/s1600/647.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-neh7haio0ZA%2FV4Okf-cfm8I%2FAAAAAAAABGs%2FtgDJnGJP7kQObdMY8bHUiZTMv8i_1YRrgCLcB%2Fs1600%2F647.jpeg&h=9fd3ce32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5、You sure? Yes yes，is here.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-LopwoG-YIaA/V4Ok8WRT_WI/AAAAAAAABGw/GutGdasjoJE4CUdtC9TcCmfatSJ8ePlcgCLcB/s1600/648.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-LopwoG-YIaA%2FV4Ok8WRT_WI%2FAAAAAAAABGw%2FGutGdasjoJE4CUdtC9TcCmfatSJ8ePlcgCLcB%2Fs1600%2F648.jpeg&h=03203d32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 6、對於年齡尚小還不能懂事的，美軍也有賞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-TLC-W8ED55U/V4Olewsw2YI/AAAAAAAABG8/GykVttcpJyIKIizd7PIqQ8l3If9BL_87QCLcB/s1600/649.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-TLC-W8ED55U%2FV4Olewsw2YI%2FAAAAAAAABG8%2FGykVttcpJyIKIizd7PIqQ8l3If9BL_87QCLcB%2Fs1600%2F649.jpeg&h=9b6c16a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7.   少年報告美軍，前面有Ｘ匪殘餘埋伏<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.bimg.126.net/photo/HwcFiYalOj_2klBnxpuAIw==/5735615600433130736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.bimg.126.net%2Fphoto%2FHwcFiYalOj_2klBnxpuAIw%3D%3D%2F5735615600433130736.jpg&h=56d49488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.   帶完路，有賞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.bimg.126.net/photo/-SjCgPYyVZltuda7UX16pQ==/5735615600433130738.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.bimg.126.net%2Fphoto%2F-SjCgPYyVZltuda7UX16pQ%3D%3D%2F5735615600433130738.jpg&h=95b7ce48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9.    一人帶路，全家有賞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.bimg.126.net/photo/uO2rQSa1xAQtU651uydHxg==/5735615600433130740.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.bimg.126.net%2Fphoto%2FuO2rQSa1xAQtU651uydHxg%3D%3D%2F5735615600433130740.jpg&h=ba039f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10.   帶完路，你和美軍就是朋友了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.bimg.126.net/photo/vY07eZEZH4hG90j_x-O0hA==/5735615600433130741.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.bimg.126.net%2Fphoto%2FvY07eZEZH4hG90j_x-O0hA%3D%3D%2F5735615600433130741.jpg&h=0645591f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.bimg.126.net/photo/7IbK3gSFvvlG6pgVVSA6fA==/5735615600433130745.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.bimg.126.net%2Fphoto%2F7IbK3gSFvvlG6pgVVSA6fA%3D%3D%2F5735615600433130745.jpg&h=9a9804bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n帶路不分年齡。一人帶路，全家光榮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s9.sinaimg.cn/middle/5a1c70bfg96972682caf8&amp;690\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs9.sinaimg.cn%2Fmiddle%2F5a1c70bfg96972682caf8%26690&h=a1b84301&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉載：<a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_5a1c70bf0100o4se.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.sina.com.cn%2Fs%2Fblog_5a1c70bf0100o4se.html&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1EtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=45a6a8bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_5a1c70bf0100o4se.html</a>"},{"pid":"49ab4e3fb71343009b20abc48ac17b56cec72a8e","tid":1013492,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a90bf1a72a45c0be69fc942038d6dc4ba009f794","tid":1013492,"uid":204929,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7cc78fc349aadadbc57f9f93de2d78dc0cdad10e","tid":1013492,"uid":8257,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"5e8d051c6d36792f48bb4bf5eb5402e786f0db8f","tid":1013492,"uid":204929,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:45:39.000Z","msg":"2萬喺HKD定USD?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:47:57.000Z","msg":"HKD <br />\n如果2萬幾美金月薪 同總領事同級咁滯喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:51:59.000Z","msg":"有冇得加人工㗎?<br />\n如果唔係，長遠嚟講係好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:52:44.000Z","msg":"跟pt跳 4萬幾係max<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":